<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.6.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2018-03-28T14:05:31+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/</id><title type="html">끄적끄적</title><subtitle>이런저런 기술관련 이야기들</subtitle><entry><title type="html">[crossBrowsing] safari 에서 가로스크롤 막기</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/frontend/2018/03/22/iosXScroll.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="[crossBrowsing] safari 에서 가로스크롤 막기" /><published>2018-03-22T13:18:00+09:00</published><updated>2018-03-22T13:18:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/frontend/2018/03/22/iosXScroll</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/frontend/2018/03/22/iosXScroll.html">&lt;h4 id=&quot;문제&quot;&gt;문제&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-css highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;body&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;overflow-x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;hidden&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;위와 같이 &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;body&lt;/code&gt; 태그에 &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;overflow-x: hidden;&lt;/code&gt; 를 적용하면 가로스크롤이 동작하지 않아야 하지만 사파리에서는 아래와 같이 여전히 가로스크롤이 동작하는 문제
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;/images/safari.gif&quot; alt=&quot;iOS safari 에서 가로스크롤 문제&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;데스크탑&amp;amp;모바일 사파리 모두 동일한 문제 발생&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;크롬&amp;amp;파폭은 정상
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;해결책&quot;&gt;해결책&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;아래와 같이 &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;html&lt;/code&gt; 태그에도 &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;overflow-x: hidden;&lt;/code&gt; 를 추가하니 해결 됨&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;language-css highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;html&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&quot;nl&quot;&gt;overflow-x&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;hidden&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;ref&quot;&gt;Ref.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thewordcracker.com/miscellaneous/모바일-기기에서-수평-스크롤-없애기&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.thewordcracker.com/miscellaneous/모바일-기기에서-수평-스크롤-없애기&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">문제 body { overflow-x: hidden; } 위와 같이 body 태그에 overflow-x: hidden; 를 적용하면 가로스크롤이 동작하지 않아야 하지만 사파리에서는 아래와 같이 여전히 가로스크롤이 동작하는 문제 데스크탑&amp;amp;모바일 사파리 모두 동일한 문제 발생 크롬&amp;amp;파폭은 정상</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">requirejs 모듈 로드시 순서 관련</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/memo/2018/03/22/requirejs.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="requirejs 모듈 로드시 순서 관련" /><published>2018-03-22T00:46:36+09:00</published><updated>2018-03-22T00:46:36+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/memo/2018/03/22/requirejs</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/memo/2018/03/22/requirejs.html">&lt;h4 id=&quot;예시&quot;&gt;예시&lt;/h4&gt;
